{
	{
		dim3 blocks((7 + 1), 1, 1);
		dim3 threads((2 + 1), 1, 1);
		_kernel_1<<<blocks, threads>>>(c3, B1_prop_i, B1_prop_r, B2_prop_i, B2_prop_r, buf_BB_H_new_term_b1_i, buf_BB_H_new_term_b1_r, buf_BB_H_new_term_b2_i, buf_BB_H_new_term_b2_r, buf_C_BB_H_prop_i, buf_C_BB_H_prop_r, buf_C_i, buf_C_r, buf_flip_BB_H_new_term_b1_i, buf_flip_BB_H_new_term_b1_r, buf_flip_BB_H_new_term_b2_i, buf_flip_BB_H_new_term_b2_r, buf_flip_src_B1_Blocal_r1_i, buf_flip_src_B1_Blocal_r1_r, buf_flip_src_B1_Blocal_r2_i, buf_flip_src_B1_Blocal_r2_r, buf_flip_src_B2_Blocal_r1_i, buf_flip_src_B2_Blocal_r1_r, buf_flip_src_B2_Blocal_r2_i, buf_flip_src_B2_Blocal_r2_r, buf_src_B1_Blocal_diquark_r1_i, buf_src_B1_Blocal_diquark_r1_r, buf_src_B1_Blocal_diquark_r2_i, buf_src_B1_Blocal_diquark_r2_r, buf_src_B1_Blocal_props_r1_i, buf_src_B1_Blocal_props_r1_r, buf_src_B1_Blocal_props_r2_i, buf_src_B1_Blocal_props_r2_r, buf_src_B1_Blocal_r1_i, buf_src_B1_Blocal_r1_r, buf_src_B1_Blocal_r2_i, buf_src_B1_Blocal_r2_r, buf_src_B2_Blocal_diquark_r1_i, buf_src_B2_Blocal_diquark_r1_r, buf_src_B2_Blocal_diquark_r2_i, buf_src_B2_Blocal_diquark_r2_r, buf_src_B2_Blocal_props_r1_i, buf_src_B2_Blocal_props_r1_r, buf_src_B2_Blocal_props_r2_i, buf_src_B2_Blocal_props_r2_r, buf_src_B2_Blocal_r1_i, buf_src_B2_Blocal_r1_r, buf_src_B2_Blocal_r2_i, buf_src_B2_Blocal_r2_r, hex_snk_color_weights, hex_snk_psi_i, hex_snk_psi_r, hex_snk_spin_weights, hex_snk_weights, sigs, src_color_weights, src_psi_B1_i, src_psi_B1_r, src_psi_B2_i, src_psi_B2_r, src_spin_block_weights, src_spin_weights, src_spins, src_weights);
	};
	return 0;
};
